{"talk":{"id":28164,"name":"Gabby Rivera: The story of Marvel's first queer Latina superhero","description":"With Marvel's \"America Chavez,\" Gabby Rivera wrote a new kind of superhero -- one who can punch portals into other dimensions while also embracing her gentle, goofy, soft side. In a funny, personal talk, Rivera shares how her own childhood as a queer Puerto Rican in the Bronx informed this new narrative -- and shows images from the comic book that reveal what happens when a superhero embraces her humanity. As she says: \"That myth of having to go it alone and be tough is not serving us.\"","slug":"gabby_rivera_the_story_of_marvel_s_first_queer_latina_superhero","recorded_at":"2018-11-08 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-11-29 15:56:18","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:42:21","viewed_count":1094146,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":571,"name":"TED Salon: Radical Craft"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2a2202dab38d6af06a8a5d3e8f91c4e3db49e12e_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2a2202dab38d6af06a8a5d3e8f91c4e3db49e12e_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2a2202dab38d6af06a8a5d3e8f91c4e3db49e12e_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2a2202dab38d6af06a8a5d3e8f91c4e3db49e12e_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/83cc93eb22d14f89e35c6baebd6bb71349925153_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GabbyRivera_2018S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":5585471,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GabbyRivera_2018S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":15462246,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GabbyRivera_2018S-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b4